Mr. Ribble (for himself, Mr. Ryan of Wisconsin, Mr. Pocan, Mr. Rokita, Mr. Schrader, and Mr. Duffy) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the Committee on the Budget, and in addition to the Committees on Rules and Oversight and Government Reform, for a period to be subsequently determined by the Speaker, in each case for consideration of such provisions as fall within the jurisdiction of the committee concerned
Referral to the Committee on Rules extended for a period ending not later than December 11, 2014
